  "body": "In a K8s environment a container that is migrating a production database might be expected to take a considerable amount of time. Currently since these migration tools disallow reporting a healthy liveness during migrations. This could cause K8s to kill and restart the container during the migration.\r\n\r\nDuring migrations the Liveness should be reported as healthy while Readiness should be reported unhealthy. This would ensure K8s always allows the correct amount of time for migrations.",
